Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.53,0:25:43.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎杰米成为唯一的人身监护人\N{\r原文字幕}Jamie was made the sole conservator of the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:46.37,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎他不得不与法院指定的 ‎一位名为安德鲁瓦雷特的律师\N{\r原文字幕}He had to share the conservatorship of the estate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.46,0:25:49.67,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎共享资产的监护权\N{\r原文字幕}with a court-appointed attorney named Andrew Wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:56.30,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎杰米有破产问题\N{\r原文字幕}You had Jamie who had bankruptcy issues
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.38,0:25:59.43,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎他在自己的生活中对财务管理不当\N{\r原文字幕}and financial mismanagement of his own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.51,0:26:03.35,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎他们说：“我们有安德鲁瓦雷特 ‎作为共同监护人\N{\r原文字幕}and they said, "We have Andrew Wallet here as the co-conservator,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.43,0:26:05.27,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎而且会有信托利益”\N{\r原文字幕}and has a fiduciary interest,"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.35,0:26:06.85,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎但在法庭文件中\N{\r原文字幕}but in court documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.94,0:26:10.56,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎他谈到了监护权 ‎将其视为一种“混合商业模式”\N{\r原文字幕}he talked about the conservatorship as being a "hybrid business model."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.65,0:26:11.90,译文字幕,tag,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}混合商业模式
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:22.78,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎根据2008年2月6日 ‎向法院提交的文件\N{\r原文字幕}According to the papers filed with the court on February 6, 2008,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.87,0:26:25.70,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎监护人有权查阅 ‎与布兰妮的个人资产有关的\N{\r原文字幕}the conservators have access to all documents and records
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.79,0:26:27.54,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎所有文件和记录\N{\r原文字幕}related to Britney's estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.62,0:26:31.50,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎他们可以进入并占有 ‎她的房子 把人赶出去\N{\r原文字幕}They can enter and take possession of her house, kick people out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.59,0:26:35.01,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎发布限制令 雇佣保安\N{\r原文字幕}they can issue restraining orders, and employ security guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.09,0:26:37.88,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎用布兰妮的钱支付涉及资产事宜的\N{\r原文字幕}they can use Britney's money to pay attorneys for matters
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:41.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎律师费用 开办和经营企业\N{\r原文字幕}involving the estate, open and operate businesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.80,0:26:44.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,‎雇人担任任何必要的职位\N{\r原文字幕}hire people for any position necessary,
